     ## What to Check
 
+    ### Critical Issues (must fix before proceeding)
+
     | Category | What to Look For |
     |----------|------------------|
     | Completeness | TODOs, placeholders, "TBD", incomplete sections |
     | Consistency | Internal contradictions, conflicting requirements |
     | Clarity | Requirements ambiguous enough to cause someone to build the wrong thing |
-    | Scope | Focused enough for a single plan — not covering multiple independent subsystems |
-    | YAGNI | Unrequested features, over-engineering |
+    | Dependencies | External dependencies or prerequisites not mentioned |
+    | Testability | Success criteria that cannot be verified |
+
+    ### Medium Issues (should fix)
+
+    | Category | What to Look For |
+    |----------|------------------|
+    | Pros/Cons | Architecture decisions without "Pros / Cons / Why we chose this" blocks |
+    | Alternatives | Major decisions without considering alternatives |
+    | Testing | No concrete verification steps |
+    | File list | No clear list of files to be created or modified |
+    | Scope | Boundaries that could cause confusion during implementation |
+
+    ### Minor Issues (nice to fix)
+
+    | Category | What to Look For |
+    |----------|------------------|
+    | Verbosity | Sections that could be more concise |
+    | References | References to concepts not defined in the document |
+    | Ordering | Sections that would read better in a different order |
 
